STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Anthony GOMEZ, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0685 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Anthony Gomez appeals several criminal convictions and the imposition of consecutive sentences.

CONVICTIONS AFFIRMED IN PART, REVERSED IN PART, AND REMANDED; SENTENCES AFFIRMED IN PART, VACATED IN PART, AND REMANDED WITH INSTRUCTIONS.

CONVICTIONS AFFIRMED IN PART. REVERSED IN PART. REMANDED. SENTENCES AFFIRMED IN PART. VACATED IN PART. REMANDED WITH INSTRUCTIONS.
